{"tid":598020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊岳橋：國歌法條文不應有模糊　避免執法標準不一","createTime":"2018-03-19T07:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-20T13:16:29.000Z","uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"4d6de48eec8462178b73ec108eeee0847a5b9704","tid":598020,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:07:09.000Z","msg":"政府上星期向立法會提交《國歌法》本地立法建議。公民黨黨魁楊岳橋認為，建議中有關篡改、歪曲和貶損的定義較為主觀，擔心立法後，市民容易誤墮法網。楊岳橋在本台節目《千禧年代》說，條文應讓市民清楚明白做了甚麼才犯法，不應有模糊之處，避免執法標準不一。<br />\n<br />\n出席節目的經民聯立法會議員梁美芬相信，普通法對篡改、歪曲和貶損的定義都有成熟的原則處理，又認為執法人員有能力區分有關行為是否故意，相信無心貶損者不會犯法。梁美芬又說，市民在《國歌法》本地立法後，二次創作國歌會有一定風險，建議市民不應利用國歌做二次創作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386571-20180319.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386571-20180319.htm&d=oK81T%2BzW%2FRBjANvf%2FMit2W6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c2913724\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386571-20180319.htm&h=309799ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386571-20180319.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f8f572b897bd506a4aa32744fdfc19742e3b8a","tid":598020,"uid":4783,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:09:10.000Z","msg":"原來公民黨先係焦土派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2127760279a8b02722c0e99c67134be61f6c461d","tid":598020,"uid":6964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae16b1d58d64ef410d31dd73d97b1059fd27004c","tid":598020,"uid":170157,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"re